Below is a **Markdown version of the SDDD** (Software‑Driven Design Document) for your **Access → Power Platform** order number reservation system. It’s written to be **implementation-ready** (schema, flows, UX, security, ALM, Copilot playbook), and it reflects every decision we locked in during our Q\&A.

