### 11.1 Environments

*   DEV → TEST/UAT → PROD

### 11.2 Solutions

*   Single solution containing:
    *   Dataverse tables + keys
    *   Canvas app
    *   Power Automate flows
    *   Security roles

### 11.3 Configuration & Seed Data

*   Seed QualifierType in DEV and deploy with solution
