## 12. Migration Plan (Access → Dataverse)

### 12.1 What to migrate

*   Optional historical ledger (existing SalesOrders records)
*   Initialize counters:
    *   SalesBaseTokenCounter.NextBaseToken = next value after last used SALES base
    *   Sequence counters can be initialized as needed; otherwise they will start at 1 per stream when first used
*   Import Customers (from ERP extract)
*   Import QualifierType list

### 12.2 Validation Tests

*   Allocate batch with multiple qualifiers
*   Parallel commits from two users (concurrency test)
*   Create multiple backorders on same root
*   Cancel and reactivate
*   Verify no duplicates possible by attempting intentional collisions

