## 13. Copilot Playbook (Build Acceleration + Guardrails)

### 13.1 Safe Uses

*   Scaffold tables and relationships
*   Generate Canvas UI layout
*   Create Flow skeletons (triggers, inputs, responses)

### 13.2 Unsafe Uses (Do Not Delegate)

*   Allocator math
*   Retry/hard-stop semantics
*   Alternate keys / uniqueness constraints
*   Backorder derivation rules

