OrderSequenceCounter(Scope choice SALES/PROJECT, BaseToken, QualifierCode, SystemLetter, NextSeq, LastUpdated),
AllocatedOrderNumber(Scope, BaseToken, QualifierCode, SystemLetter, Seq, BackorderNo, OrderNumber, ParentOrder lookup to AllocatedOrderNumber, BatchId, CustomerCode, CustomerName, PONumber, DateReceived, ActiveFlag, DateCreated, DateBilled, DateInvoiceSent, DateCanceled, CancelReason, CanceledBy, DateReactivated, ReactivatedBy).

Do not invent allocation logic. Provide recommended data types, required flags, and note where alternate keys should be created.
```

