- Batch Generate screen with required Customer/PO/DateReceived/SystemLetter and a qualifier quantity grid
- Preview button calling a flow and showing a disclaimer
- Commit button calling a flow and showing created OrderNumbers

Do not compute sequences in Power Apps. All allocation is performed by Power Automate.
```

#### Prompt: Flow Skeletons Only

```text
Create Power Automate flow skeletons with Power Apps trigger + Response action for:
SO.PreviewBatch, SO.CommitBatch, SO.CreateBackorder, SO.CancelOrder, SO.ReactivateOrder, SO.StampBilled, SO.StampInvoiceSent.
