# Appendix A — Formatting Rules

*   Seq: 3 digits (`001`, `002`, …)
*   BackorderNo: 2 digits (`00`, `01`, …)

OrderNumber construction:

    OrderNumber =
      BaseToken & "-" &
      QualifierCode & SystemLetter & Text(Seq, "000") & "-" &
      Text(BackorderNo, "00")

